run start server : $ deno run --allow-net --allow-read server.js

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

for ubuntu: sudo /home/user/.deno/bin/deno run --allow-net --allow-read server.js
change "user" for your user name

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

https://github.com/chibat/heroku-deno-getting-started
create buildpack heroku deno:
heroku create --buildpack https://github.com/chibat/heroku-buildpack-deno.git